title: Similar to Interstate, can't figure this typeface out.
author: msohio

comments.content: I’d say DIN. Someone else probably could tell exactly which cut of it.

Agree with Riccardo. Parachute’s DIN Text Medium should do the trick:  
 [http://www.parachute.gr/typefaces/allfonts/din-text-pro](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317091532/http:/www.parachute.gr/typefaces/allfonts/din-text-pro "http://www.parachute.gr/typefaces/allfonts/din-text-pro")
